Module io.github.jonloucks.metalog.api
Package io.github.jonloucks.metalog.api

Interface Entities

All Known Subinterfaces:
Entities.Builder<B>
public interface Entities
Contains zero or more Entity instances Supports both unique and duplicate entities, determined by the entity name and unique fields. Examples of unique entities are "thread", "time", and "thrown" Examples of non-unique entities could be "event" where there are multiple events associated with a log
